Martha Ceramic Eye-Catching Leaking Paint Detail Table Lamp

The contemporary look of the Martha Ceramic Table Lamp makes it a statement piece in your home. With a durable ceramic base, a simple linen shade and an eye-catching leaking paint detail. Perfect for the living room or bedroom. Indoor use only. Compatible with E27/Max 60W light bulbs.

Attractive and stylish, this Scandi-style floor lamp is a fresh update for your interior. It has a 2-tone stand with a weighty round base. The coordinating fabric drum shade completes the look.

Features:

  • E27, requires 1 x max. 60W bulb
  • Lightbulb not included
  • E14, requires 1 x max. 40W bulb
  • Switch type: inline switch
  • The stand is made of metal.

Product Details:

  • Style: Casual; Scandinavian
  • Assembly Required: Yes

Dimensions:

  • Overall: 155cm H x 35cm W x 35cm D
  • Overall Product Weight: 3.6 Kilograms
